{"article_id":"ZbVVX5w85Vx1Oq57","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In Washington this week , calls","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to fix the problem","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"of people","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"getting insurance cancellation notices","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"are getting louder","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"and coming from all sides .","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"But turning back the clock on health insurance cancellations turns out to be a lot harder","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"than it sounds .","depth":3},{"id":8,"text":"Republicans have been blasting the president for weeks","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"about breaking his promise","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"that people would be able to keep their insurance policies .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Later this week , the GOP-led House will vote on a bill","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"called the Keep Your Health Plan Act .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"What 's changing is that Democrats are now starting to join the chorus .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"Last week , Sen. Mary Landrieu , D-La. ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"who 's facing a tough re-election bid next fall ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"introduced legislation","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"aimed at letting more people keep their plans .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"`` We said to people :","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"If you had insurance","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"that you liked","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"you could keep it , ''","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"she said on the Senate floor .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"`` We did n't say :","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"If you had insurance","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"that you liked","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"that did n't meet the minimum standards ,","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"or met the minimum standards ,","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"you could keep it .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"We just said ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"and the president said , over and over ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"'If you have insurance","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"and you like the insurance","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"you have ,","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"you can keep it . ' That is the single focus of my bill . ''","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"On Tuesday , former President Bill Clinton ,","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"who 's been dubbed the explainer in chief for the health law ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"added his backing .","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"`` I personally believe ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"even if it takes a change in the law ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"that the president should honor the commitment","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"the federal government made to those people","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and let them keep what they got , ''","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"he said in an interview with the online magazine Ozy.com .","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"Even President Obama himself has hinted","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"that he wants to do something about the problem","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"of people","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"getting their policies canceled .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"`` I am deeply concerned about it , ''","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"he told NBC 's Chuck Todd last week ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"`` and I have assigned my team","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"to see what we can do","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"to close some of the holes and gaps in the law . ''","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"So far , though , the administration has n't proposed anything specific for those people in the individual insurance market","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"getting cancellation notices .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"And there 's a good reason for that ,","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"say industry experts .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"The bottom line is that it 's simply too late to undo those canceled policies .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"`` It 's not at all feasible , ''","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"says Robert Laszewski , president of the consulting firm Health Policy and Strategy Associates .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"`` It would be wonderful .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"I 'm one of the people","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"who got my policy canceled .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"I would like to keep it ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"but we ca n't get that fix in place in 45 days . ''","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"That 45 days is between now and Jan. 1 ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"when the new standards under the Affordable Care Act kick in .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Laszewski says","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"the insurance industry has spent most of the past year","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"getting ready for this .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"They 've rewritten policies ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"gotten them approved by state regulators ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"and found and updated information with their policyholders .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"`` Even if you decide to go 'never mind ' about all these cancellations , ''","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"he says ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"`` how is the insurance company going to send out letters to all these people within the space of a couple of weeks ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"rejigger all of their computer systems","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"that took months","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"to redo in the first place ,","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"and get these people to decide","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"whether they want to try for Obamacare ,","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"which is the only place","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"they can get subsidies ,","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"or try to stay on their own policies ? ''","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Joel Ario , managing director at the consulting firm Manatt Health Solutions , is n't quite so negative .","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"He says","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"that just this week in California , two insurers have agreed to continue to offer some existing plans , at least temporarily .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"But that 's a bit of a different situation ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"he says ,","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"because they settled with the state 's insurance commissioner .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"`` Their earlier cancellations were not proper under California law , ''","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"says Ario ,","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"`` and they are extending their policies","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"- in one case [ by ] another couple months , and in another case [ by ] three months .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"So clearly it can be done by the carriers","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"to extend current coverages . ''","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"But Ario ,","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"who earlier headed the federal government 's health exchange program ,","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"says","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"if the insurance companies did everything correctly ,","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"it would n't be fair to require them to extend their current policies at their current rates .","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"`` If they were to continue coverages ,","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"they would ask for a rate increase , ''","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"he says .","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"`` Typically in the individual market there are significant rate increases on a year-to-year basis . ''","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Many people would actually do better financially in the exchanges with a tax credit ,","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"Ario says ,","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"rather than stick with their current policy with an inflation increase .","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"They just do n't realize that","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"because they have n't been able to get on the website yet","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"to see .","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"Which brings the question back to where the Affordable Care Act has been since October :","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"Can the federal government get its balky website up and running at full strength fast enough","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"for a critical mass of those canceled policyholders to figure out","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"they might be OK after all ?","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":229,"left":122,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":120,"right":121,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":120,"left":119,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":119,"left":118,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":0,"right":117,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":1,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":148,"right":227,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":124,"right":147,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":8,"right":123,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":125,"right":146,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":13,"right":145,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":128,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":17,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":126,"right":16,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":132,"right":143,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":132,"left":131,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":18,"right":130,"relation":"attr